commit.title: Simplify and fix the libobject of Argument Scopes
commit.message:
Simplify and fix the libobject of Argument Scopes

We do not change the semantics, except fixing #10212. In particular, we keep
the dynamic binding effect `Bind Scope` has on argument scopes.

Fixes #10212.
